<h1>Ember Data async relationships examples</h1>

<p>Hi, this is an example blog to showcase different ways that ember-data loads relationships.</p>

<h2>Posts</h2>

{{#each model as |post|}}
  <div class="post">
    <h3>{{post.title}}</h3>
    <p>{{post.body}}</p>

    <h4>Comments</h4>
    <ul>
      {{#each post.comments as |comment|}}
        <li>{{comment.message}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </div>
{{/each}}

{{outlet}}
